<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EcoBin - Smart E-Waste Recycling</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/sections.css">
    <div class="cat-icon icon-green"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-button"></i></div>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include("./navbar.ejs") %>

    <header id="home" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i> AI-Powered Smart Recycling</div>
            <h1>Recycle E-Waste.<br><span class="green-text">Earn Rewards.</span><br>Save the Planet.</h1>
            <p>Find smart bins near you, let AI detect your e-waste, and get rewarded for every item you recycle. Making sustainability simple and rewarding.</p>
            <div class="hero-btns">
                <a class="btn-green" href="/findBin"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-crosshairs"></i> Find Nearest Bin <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                <a class="btn-glass" href="/recycle"><i class="fa-solid fa-expand"></i> Recycle E-Waste</a>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat"><h3>50K+</h3><p>Items Recycled</p></div>
        <div class="stat"><h3>200+</h3><p>Smart Bins</p></div>
        <div class="stat"><h3>10K+</h3><p>Happy Users</p></div>
    </div>

    <section id="features" class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="tag">Features</span>
            <h2>Everything You Need for Smart Recycling</h2>
            <p>A complete ecosystem designed to make e-waste recycling effortless, transparent, and rewarding.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-circle green"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i></div>
                <h3>Smart Bin Locator</h3>
                <p>Find the nearest e-waste bin based on what you want to recycle. Real-time availability and directions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-circle blue"><i class="fa-solid fa-microchip"></i></div>
                <h3>AI Detection</h3>
                <p>Drop your e-waste and watch our AI instantly identify the item and calculate its recycling value.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-circle orange"><i class="fa-solid fa-gift"></i></div>
                <h3>Earn Rewards</h3>
                <p>Get points for every item you recycle. Redeem for discounts, vouchers, or eco-friendly products.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="how-it-works" class="section light-gray">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="tag-pill">How It Works</span>
            <h2 class="title-main">Simple as <span class="green-text">1-2-3</span></h2>
            <p class="subtitle">From finding a bin to earning rewards - the entire process takes less than 3 minutes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-container">
            <div class="central-line"></div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item left">
                <div class="timeline-content card-3d">
                    <span class="step-number">01</span>
                    <h3>Select E-Waste Type</h3>
                    <p>Choose what you want to recycle - phones, batteries, laptops, chargers, or cables.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-dot"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen"></i></div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item right">
                <div class="timeline-content card-3d">
                    <span class="step-number">02</span>
                    <h3>Find Nearest Bin</h3>
                    <p>Instantly see compatible bins near you with real-time availability and directions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-dot"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i></div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item left">
                <div class="timeline-content card-3d">
                    <span class="step-number">03</span>
                    <h3>Upload Image And details </h3>
                    <p>Identify yourself at the bin by scanning your unique QR code on the screen.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-dot"><i class="fa-solid fa-qrcode"></i></div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item right">
                <div class="timeline-content card-3d">
                    <span class="step-number">04</span>
                    <h3>Drop Your Item and Verify</h3>
                    <p>Place your e-waste in the bin and watch AI detect and evaluate your item.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-dot"><i class="fa-solid fa-expand"></i></div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item left">
                <div class="timeline-content card-3d">
                    <span class="step-number">05</span>
                    <h3>Collect Rewards</h3>
                    <p>Earn points based on item value. Redeem for discounts and eco-friendly products.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-dot"><i class="fa-solid fa-gift"></i></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="done-badge">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Done! You've made a difference.
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="items" class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="tag-pill">Accepted Items</span>
            <h2 class="title-main">What Can You <span class="green-text">Recycle?</span></h2>
            <p class="subtitle">We accept all types of electronic waste. Click on any category to learn more.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="category-scroll-wrapper">
    <div class="category-grid" id="category-list">
        <div class="cat-card active" onclick="updateItem('smartphones', this)">
            <div class="cat-icon icon-green"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen"></i></div>
            <p>Smartphones</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card" onclick="updateItem('batteries', this)">
            <div class="cat-icon icon-orange"><i class="fa-solid fa-battery-half"></i></div>
            <p>Batteries</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card" onclick="updateItem('laptops', this)">
            <div class="cat-icon icon-purple"><i class="fa-solid fa-laptop"></i></div>
            <p>Laptops</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card" onclick="updateItem('cables', this)">
            <div class="cat-icon icon-teal"><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i></div>
            <p>Cables</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card" onclick="updateItem('chargers', this)">
            <div class="cat-icon icon-red"><i class="fa-solid fa-plug"></i></div>
            <p>Chargers</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card" onclick="updateItem('audio', this)">
            <div class="cat-icon icon-indigo"><i class="fa-solid fa-headphones"></i></div>
            <p>Audio Devices</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card" onclick="updateItem('wearables', this)">
    <div class="cat-icon icon-pink">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i>
    </div>
    <p>Wearables</p>
</div>

<div class="cat-card" onclick="updateItem('gaming', this)">
    <div class="cat-icon icon-bright-green">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-gamepad"></i>
    </div>
    <p>Gaming Devices</p>
</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="detail-display-box grad-blue" id="detail-box">
    <div class="detail-header">
        <div class="detail-icon-large" id="main-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen"></i></div>
        <div>
            <h3 id="item-title">Smartphones</h3>
            <p id="item-desc">Old phones, feature phones, and mobile devices</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-item">
            <label>Estimated Value</label>
            <p id="item-value">â‚¹50 - â‚¹500</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
            <label>Environmental Impact</label>
            <p id="item-impact">Recovers rare earth metals and reduces toxic waste</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    </section>
    <section id="impact" class="section dark-impact">
    <div class="section-header">
        <span class="tag-outline">Our Collective Impact</span>
        <h2 class="white-text">Together, We're Making a <span class="green-text">Difference</span></h2>
        <p class="white-text opacity-8">Every item you recycle contributes to a cleaner planet. See the impact our community has made together.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-card">
            <div class="impact-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash-can"></i></div>
            <div class="impact-data">
                <h3>25,000 kg</h3>
                <p>E-Waste Recycled</p>
                <span>Electronics safely processed</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
            <div class="impact-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-cloud"></i></div>
            <div class="impact-data">
                <h3>15,000 kg COâ‚‚</h3>
                <p>Emissions Prevented</p>
                <span>Carbon footprint reduced</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
            <div class="impact-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-droplet"></i></div>
            <div class="impact-data">
                <h3>500,000 L</h3>
                <p>Water Saved</p>
                <span>From reduced mining</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
            <div class="impact-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-tree"></i></div>
            <div class="impact-data">
                <h3>2,500 trees</h3>
                <p>Equivalent Impact</p>
                <span>In carbon absorption</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="join-banner">
        <p>Join <strong>10,000+</strong> eco-warriors</p>
        <span>Be part of the movement towards a sustainable future</span>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-box">
        <span class="cta-tag">ðŸŒ± Start Your Recycling Journey</span>
        <h2>Ready to Make a Difference?</h2>
        <p>Find your nearest smart bin, recycle your e-waste, and start earning rewards today. Every item counts towards a cleaner, greener planet.</p>
        <a class="btn-green-large" href="/findBin"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Find Nearest Bin Now</a>
        <div class="cta-features">
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> 200+ Active Bins</span>
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> AI-Powered Detection</span>
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Instant Rewards</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
    <%- include("./footer.ejs") %>
    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>

</body>
</html>